      "raw_text": "Hold up your hand and repeat\nafter me, Never again!'\"\n\n\nThus spake Recorder Mara In\nBayonne, NJ j., to Thomas Collins,\nwho had been arrested for being\ndrunk and said he wanted to swear\noff. -- ,,.\n\n\nNever again.\" solemnly shouted\nCollins, with his right hand elevated\nand as loudly as his parched throat\nwould permit. Thus ended what is\nbelieved to be the shortest and most\nup-to-date temperance pledge on\nrecord."
